Pavel Machek wrote:
> 
> Okay; which mem= options you want killed?
> 
Anything that doesn't match the regexp (in Perl syntax):
/^mem=(0[0-7]*|[1-9][0-9]*|0x[0-9a-f]+)[kmg]$/i
> What about this?
Looks good to me.
> 								Pavel
> 
